title: Find the One Ring
notes: Task to locate the One Ring and ensure it remains hidden from Sauron.

title: Journey to Rivendell
notes: Travel with the hobbits to Rivendell for the council meeting.

title: Form the Fellowship
notes: Gather a group of allies to form the Fellowship of the Ring.

title: Travel to Mordor
notes: Lead the Fellowship towards Mordor to destroy the One Ring.

title: Battle at Helm's Deep
notes: Prepare the defenses and lead the forces of Rohan against Saruman's army.

title: Secure the Shire
notes: Ensure the Shire is protected from the threats of the outside world.

title: Scout the Paths of the Dead
notes: Gather intelligence on the Paths of the Dead and report any unusual activities.

title: Forge New Alliances
notes: Reach out to potential allies in distant lands to strengthen our position against Sauron.

title: Reforge the Sword
notes: Oversee the reforging of Narsil, the sword that cut the One Ring from Sauron's hand.

title: Gather Herbs for Healing
notes: Collect athelas and other healing herbs to aid the wounded after battles.
